<div class="border rounded" style="color: whitesmoke; background-color: #3db8ff; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p>Artist added successfully.</p>
</div>
<div style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2>Add your favourite artist here!</h2>
</div>
